{"tid":2299623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，見到掣就忍唔住好想撳？","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T03:10:11.000Z","uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96d03a6621043c2b8fb7037f2cf775a18e617441","tid":2299623,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"每次喺街度見到掣，例如扶手電梯嘅緊急剎停掣，都會蠢蠢欲動（當然因為諗到後果冇撳落去，亦奉勸大家唔好咁做）<br />\n最近呢個情況好似嚴重咗，例如同女朋友一齊返屋企，女朋友開緊門嗰陣，我都會忍唔住係咁撳門鐘，佢開門同時，我係咁叮噹叮噹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣算唔算係強逼症一種？"},{"pid":"e22a2aa88f8875f3980a6afd306b206dcccf10e5","tid":2299623,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"算係你手多 無其他原因"},{"pid":"19bf12708d7e1c1ece48a652f8a0c4620e6d1d10","tid":2299623,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"見過你e種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1d22177a89b2baba619252934e1b2789806364","tid":2299623,"uid":93600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"好中意㩒門鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07c0a0adc57cbbfb697debc1d56d6839d9c77a8","tid":2299623,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19bf12708d7e1c1ece48a652f8a0c4620e6d1d10","tid":2299623,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"見過你e種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"樓上話我手多，你就話我痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkg